      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels less like peace and more like i'm just waiting for something to end. like i'm stuck in this weird limbo where i'm still breathing but i'm already gone. everything i do feels so pointless without him. why am i even trying to keep going when the part of me that actually lived died with him?",
